rows.label: tlk43420171_01_msg0001
rows.name:
I heard that the streets of Acedia are
as beautiful as a work of art. I'm
here from Invidia for sightseeing.

rows.label: tlk43420171_01_msg0002
rows.name:
The cathedral is majestic and the
streets are laid out beautifully...

rows.label: tlk43420171_01_msg0003
rows.name:
But the refugee camp... Well,
I suppose there's not much
that can be done about it...

rows.label: tlk43420171_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Despite all the help they get, they still
say they're against Blades? Perhaps they
should consider moving on then.
